target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_SEQ_00<tab>Der Qiqirn ist auf der Suche nach Geleitschutz.

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_TODO_01<tab>Escort the kindly Qiqirn to the Specula Imperatoris entrance.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_TODO_01<tab>Den sanftmütigen Qiqirn bis zur schweren Tür geleiten
TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_TODO_02<tab>Mit dem sanftmütigen Qiqirn vor Specula Imperatoris sprechen

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_TODO_03<tab>Pour cow bitter juice at the designated locations.

target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_TODO_05<tab>Mit dem sanftmütigen Qiqirn vor Ala Gannha sprechen

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_000<tab>Me so sad. No one listen what I have to say. Why they think me a bad Qiqirn?
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_000<tab>Qiqirn seeehr traurig sein. Niemand helfen wollen. Alle denken, Qiqirn böser Qiqirn.

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_001<tab>You will hear me? Oh, very happy to meet kindly adventurer!
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_001<tab>Du helfen wollen? Das aber sehr nett! Qiqirn freuen wie Chocobo-Küken!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_002<tab>There is a place me want to go. But lots of bad Qiqirn who stop me. Protect me, kindly adventurer!
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_002<tab>Qiqirn zu einem Ort wollen, aber draußen viele böse Qiqirn. Du Qiqirn beschützen!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_010<tab>Keep me nice and safe until reach Specula Imperatoris. Me want to explore it.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_010<tab>Qiqirn nach Specula Imperatoris wollen. Du Qiqirn bis Eingang bringen, ja?

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_SYTEM_100_010<tab>Escort the kindly Qiqirn safely to the Specula Imperatoris entrance. Should you fail to defend him, or move too far away, he will return to the Last Forest, where you may rendezvous with him before trying again.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_SYTEM_100_010<tab>Du beginnst eine Geleitschutzmission für den sanftmütigen Qiqirn. Wenn ihr zu weit voneinander getrennt werdet, kehrt dein Schützling zum Ausgangspunkt zurück. Sprich dort mit ihm, um die Mission noch einmal zu beginnen.

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_011<tab>Keep me nice and safe until reach Specula Imperatoris. Me want to explore it.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_011<tab>Qiqirn nach Specula Imperatoris wollen. Du Qiqirn bis Eingang bringen, ja?

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_BALLOON_000_012<tab>Keep me nice and safe until reach Specula Imperatoris. Me want to explore it.
TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_SYSTEM_000_014<tab>You have failed to successfully escort the kindly Qiqirn to Specula Imperatoris. Return to the Last Forest and speak with the kindly Qiqirn to begin once more.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_SYSTEM_000_014<tab>Da der sanftmütige Qiqirn von dir getrennt wurde, lässt sich die Tür nicht öffnen. Kehre zum Ausgangspunkt der Mission zurück und sprich mit dem Qiqirn, um die Mission noch einmal in Angriff zu nehmen.

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_019<tab>(-Kindly Qiqirn-)Me going to search inside. Can ask kindly adventurer to do favor in the meantime?
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_019<tab>(-Sanftmütiger Qiqirn-)Wir da sind! Qiqirn drinnen Glitzer suchen! Du in Zwischenzeit helfen!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_020<tab>Bad Qiqirn are scary. Me came up with plan to keep them away.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_020<tab>Böse Qiqirn sicher stören! Darum du das hier streu-streu machen!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_021<tab>Pour this around. All Qiqirn hate this stinky smell. So stinky and smelly it is. Meet here again when done!
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_021<tab>Qiqirn diesen Stinkeruch nicht mögen. Hält böse Qiqirn fern. Wenn fertig, hier treffen, ja?

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_030<tab>Found what me needed. Time to go home!
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_030<tab>Viel Glitzer gefunden! Schnell nach Hause gehen!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_040<tab>Thank you, kindly adventurer! Took back shiny shiny thing belonging to Qiqirn. Bad Qiqirn loot it and give loot to Empire.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_040<tab>Qiqirn danken <var 08 E905 ((Abenteurerin)) ((Abenteurer)) /var>! Böse Qiqirn hatten Glitzer gestohlen! Aber jetzt zurück!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_041<tab>Me sick of Empire! Always looting loot from Qiqirn.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_041<tab>Böse Qiqirn Glitzer an Blecheimer von Kaiser geben, um nicht auf Mütze zu kriegen! Lieber kämpfen sollen!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_043<tab>But now it is Qiqirn's again. Here is reward for kindly adventurer!
target: TEXT_STMBDZ919_02875_KIKIRUN02875_000_043<tab>Aber <var 08 E905 ((nette Abenteurerin)) ((netter Abenteurer)) /var> nett geholfen! Große Dank!
